---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pickup & Delivery | Dapper Doxie"
  description="Flexible pickup and delivery options to bring your Dapper Doxie puppy home safely."
  keywords="pickup and delivery, puppy delivery, airport pickup, door-to-door puppy delivery, Dapper Doxie"
>
  <PageHeader
    title="Pickup & Delivery"
    subtitle="Flexible options to bring your new furry family member home safely"
    breadcrumbs={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Pickup & Delivery' }
    ]}
  />

  <section class="delivery-page">
    <div class="delivery-container">
      <section class="hero-card">
        <div class="hero-media">
          <img src="/images/puppies/DUKE male 10 weeks.jpeg" alt="Dachshund puppy ready to go home" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="hero-kicker">Getting Your Puppy Home</p>
          <h2>We make it easy and safe to bring your new Dapper Doxie puppy home</h2>
          <p>
            At Dapper Doxie, we understand that our families come from near and far.
            That is why we offer flexible pickup and delivery options to ensure your new Dachshund puppy
            arrives home safely and comfortably.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block">
        <h2>Your Options</h2>
        <div class="options-grid">
          <article class="option-card">
            <h3>Personal Pickup</h3>
            <p>
              There is nothing quite like meeting your new puppy in person. Our home is open for approved buyers
              to come and personally retrieve their new furry family member.
            </p>
            <h4>What to Expect</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Meet your puppy's parents and see their environment</li>
              <li>Receive hands-on guidance for your puppy's care</li>
              <li>Get answers to all your questions in person</li>
              <li>Bond with your puppy before the journey home</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>Weekend Availability</h4>
            <p>
              Weekend pickups are welcome. We are also happy to accommodate weekday pickups
              for those who cannot make it on a weekend.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="option-card">
            <h3>Professional Delivery</h3>
            <p>
              Cannot make it to our location? No problem. We offer a professional pet delivery service
              with a dedicated pet nanny who ensures your puppy travels safely in the cabin of the plane.
            </p>
            <h4>Service Includes</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Dedicated pet nanny accompanies your puppy</li>
              <li>Puppy travels in the cabin (not cargo)</li>
              <li>Comfortable, stress-free journey</li>
              <li>Flight tracking so you can follow the journey</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>Delivery Options</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Airport Pickup:</strong> Meet your puppy at your local airport.</li>
              <li><strong>Door-to-Door:</strong> We deliver directly to your home.</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="pricing-block">
        <h2>Delivery Pricing</h2>
        <p class="pricing-intro">Our delivery service is designed to be convenient and affordable:</p>
        <div class="pricing-grid">
          <article class="price-card">
            <p class="price-amount">FREE</p>
            <h3>Personal Pickup</h3>
            <p>Visit us and take your puppy home yourself.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="price-card">
            <p class="price-amount">$250</p>
            <h3>Airport Pickup</h3>
            <p>Meet your puppy at your nearest airport.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="price-card">
            <p class="price-amount">$300</p>
            <h3>Door-to-Door</h3>
            <p>Delivery directly to your home.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block">
        <h2>How Shipping Works</h2>
        <p>Setting up delivery is simple and straightforward:</p>
        <ol class="steps-list">
          <li>
            <h3>1. Provide Your Address</h3>
            <p>
              Share your complete address: street, city, state, and zip code. Let us know whether you prefer
              airport pickup or door-to-door delivery.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>2. We Coordinate Logistics</h3>
            <p>
              Our professional pet delivery company handles all arrangements. We usually need 24-48 hours
              to finalize travel details.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>3. Receive Flight Information</h3>
            <p>
              Once booked, we share flight details including estimated arrival time and a tracking number.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>4. Welcome Your Puppy Home</h3>
            <p>
              Meet your puppy at the airport or greet them at your door. They arrive safe and ready for
              their new life.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-block">
        <h2>Visiting Policy</h2>
        <article class="policy-card">
          <h3>Important Information for Visitors</h3>
          <p>
            To protect the health of our puppies and maintain a calm environment, we do not allow drop-in visits
            from prospective buyers who have not been approved. Once you have been approved to purchase,
            you are welcome to visit and take your puppy home. This policy ensures the best experience for both
            our puppies and our committed families.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="policy-card">
          <h3>Why We Have This Policy</h3>
          <p>
            Our visiting policy exists to protect our puppies' health and well-being. Too many visitors can stress
            young puppies and potentially expose them to illness before they complete their vaccination series.
            Once you are approved, we warmly welcome you to our home to meet your new family member.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="content-block faq-block">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <ul class="faq-questions">
          <li>How far in advance should I schedule delivery?</li>
          <li>Is flying safe for puppies?</li>
          <li>What should I prepare for my puppy's arrival?</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="cta-box">
        <h3>Need help choosing pickup or delivery?</h3>
        <p>Contact us and we will help you choose the best option for your family.</p>
        <a href="mailto:info@dapperdoxiepups.com" class="btn">Email Us</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .delivery-page {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: #F7FAF7;
    font-family: var(--font-family, 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif);
  }

  .delivery-container {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-card,
  .content-block,
  .pricing-block,
  .policy-block,
  .cta-box {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .hero-card {
    overflow: hidden;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: stretch;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fdfaf7 100%);
  }

  .hero-media {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    min-height: 320px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #f4ebe2;
  }

  .hero-card img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 35%;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    padding: 2.25rem 2.3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    margin: 0;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    width: fit-content;
    background: #1F5132;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
  }

  .hero-copy h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: #143521;
    max-width: 18ch;
  }

  .hero-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #5a5a5a;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    max-width: 43ch;
  }

  .content-block,
  .pricing-block,
  .policy-block,
  .cta-box {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: #143521;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: #143521;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  h4 {
    margin: 1rem 0 0.4rem;
    color: #1F5132;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    color: #5a5a5a;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .options-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .option-card {
    background: #F7FAF7;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: #5a5a5a;
  }

  ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .pricing-intro {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .price-card {
    background: #F7FAF7;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .price-amount {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: #1F5132;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .price-card p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .steps-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .steps-list li {
    background: #F7FAF7;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1.15rem;
  }

  .steps-list h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .steps-list p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .policy-block {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .policy-card {
    background: #F7FAF7;
    border: 1px solid #e8ddd4;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .faq-questions {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .faq-questions li {
    margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #143521;
  }

  .cta-box {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1F5132, #143521);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cta-box h3,
  .cta-box p {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.45rem;
    background: #2E6B45;
    color: #143521;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: #4A8A63;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero-media {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 11;
      min-height: 260px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      padding: 1.6rem 1.5rem 1.7rem;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero-copy h2 {
      font-size: 1.65rem;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .pricing-grid,
    .options-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .delivery-page {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .hero-copy,
    .content-block,
    .pricing-block,
    .policy-block,
    .cta-box {
      padding: 1.35rem;
    }

    .hero-media {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      min-height: 220px;
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      padding: 0.32rem 0.65rem;
    }

    .hero-copy h2 {
      font-size: 1.45rem;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.45rem;
    }

    .price-amount {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
